  "title": "Symmetry perception and affective responses: a combined EEG/EMG study",
  "description": "This dataset comprises concurrent EEG and EMG recordings collected during a visual perception task examining symmetry detection and affective responses. Participants viewed visual patterns and made judgments about pattern regularity following stimulus offset, providing insights into the neural and physiological correlates of symmetry perception.",
